          "description": "It was a wonderful enlightening experience. I never knew such a treatment was available I had had surgery on my jaw. Because of this treatment It has healed up very quickly. The HBO staff was wonderful and took great care of me for 30 treatments. I never  felt so well taken care of.  Dr. Chiu is the most dynamic,  knowledgeable and positive doctor I have ever met.  I recommend this to anyone who has been told to have this treatment. It is worthwhile.",
