          "description": "Dr. Chiu and his team are fantastic! After bilateral mastectomy with immediate reconstruction for breast cancer, my breast skin was very bruised/blistered and needed serious help.\n\nThanks to the advanced wound care and oxygen therapy provided by Dr. Chiu and his team, my healing experience has been amazing and a blessing to bear witness to.\n\nThat said, search no more and rest assured that you have found the gem you\u2019re looking for! Book your appointment and witness the magic and excellent patient care experience for yourself.\n\nForever grateful, S H",
