          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL6_lUhhpWPAkNI3gZKRT3oyxg2WTdRmoezz6Co_KJnwPC7hQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "I had such a great experience while going to my Hyperbaric therapy sessions. I went it for a consult with Dr. Chiu and he expedited my process to start therapy the next day. He was great and explained everything thoroughly to me. I did 21 sessions and every time I went I was treated very well. Jenny, Erika, and Steve are all great. They are very attentive to their patients and always asked how my healing process was going. They were very professional and always made sure I felt comfortable and safe. I am so thankful to everyone that helped me and supported me through my healing process. I would 10/10 recommend this facility and Dr.Chiu.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNla3ZqTmVBEAE!2m1!1s0x0:0x17e7cae3b7334aa9!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgICekvjNeA%7C%7C?hl=en",
