          "description": "I can't rave enough about Hypebaric Treatment and Wound Center.   I had a bad wound on my entire upper jaw from surgery and it was not getting better so my Dr recommended trying the HT.   It exceeded my expectations and it was painless!     Steve, Jenny and Brian were all fantastic and most professional .  I always felt safe and cared for during my treatments.    Usually I didn't have to wait at all to go in the chamber and it was nice having a tv to watch during the treatment.    Dr Chiu runs a great center and he was also terrific.    All in all a most positive experience!",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNtdGJLWDRRRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x17e7cae3b7334aa9!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgICmtbKX4QE%7C%7C?hl=en",
